OL,3,CGorton and Denton to vote in by-
OL,4,Celection that could determine
OL,5,CStarmer's future
OL,7,FVoters in Gorton and Denton will go to
OL,8,Fthe polls on Thursday in a by-election
OL,9,Fset to provide a major test of Sir
OL,10,FKeir Starmer's leadership.
OL,12,FLabour won the seat in 2024 with more
OL,13,Fthan half the vote but polling
OL,14,Fsuggests the party's candidate
OL,15,FAngeliki Stogia faces a tight three-
OL,16,Fway contest with Reform UK's Matt
OL,17,FGoodwin and the Greens' Hannah Spencer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
