OL,3,CGorton and Denton to vote in by-
OL,4,Celection that could determine
OL,5,CStarmer's future
OL,7,FVictory would buy Sir Keir some
OL,8,Fbreathing space after a period in
OL,9,Fwhich his leadership of Labour has
OL,10,Fbeen questioned.
OL,12,FBut defeat is likely to pile the
OL,13,Fpressure back on, with some suggesting
OL,14,Fa third-placed finish in a previously
OL,15,Fsafe part of Greater Manchester could
OL,16,Fspell the end for the Prime Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
