OL,3,CGorton and Denton to vote in by-
OL,4,Celection that could determine
OL,5,CStarmer's future
OL,7,FThe party is set to throw everything
OL,8,Fat Thursday's vote with more than
OL,9,F1,000 activists expected to travel to
OL,10,Fthe constituency, which Sir Keir
OL,11,Fvisited on Monday in a sign of
OL,12,Fapparent optimism about the result.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the Greens have sought to
OL,15,Fpitch themselves as the only option
OL,16,Ffor anti-Reform voters, with Ms
OL,17,FSpencer pledging to "run the far right
OL,18,Fout of Manchester, not to come back".
OL,26,@yD@UOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
