OL,3,CGorton and Denton to vote in by-
OL,4,Celection that could determine
OL,5,CStarmer's future
OL,7,FShe said: "The polls and independent
OL,8,Ftactical voting organisation are clear
OL,9,Fthat voting Green is the only way to
OL,10,Fensure Reform don't win. We are
OL,11,Fconfident and have run a fantastic
OL,12,Fcampaign."
OL,14,FReform leader Nigel Farage also
OL,15,Fvisited the constituency on Wednesday
OL,16,Fnight, speaking to voters alongside Mr
OL,17,FGoodwin.
OL,19,FAhead of polls opening at 7am, Mr
OL,20,FFarage said: "Our message on election
OL,21,Fday is clear.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@JO]|D@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
