OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772067789
OL,3,CGorton and Denton to vote in by-
OL,4,Celection that could determine
OL,5,CStarmer's future
OL,7,F"The Prime Minister is panicking and
OL,8,Fknows he has broken his promises to
OL,9,Fthe British people.
OL,11,F"Vote Reform to ditch Starmer."
OL,13,FMr Farage's visit came a day after
OL,14,FReform suspended its interim campaign
OL,15,Fmanager Adam Mitula in the seat over
OL,16,Freports he used racist and misogynist
OL,17,Flanguage on social media. Mr Mitula
OL,18,Fhas said his remarks were "taken out
OL,19,Fof context".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUsD@_O]zD@[OU{D@KO]
